   cpr   together with james elam , he rediscovered the airway , head tilt , chin lift ( step a ) and the mouth - to-mouth breathing ( step b ) components of cpr and influenced norwegian doll maker asmund laerdal of laerdal company to design and manufacture mannequins for cpr training called resusci anne .

medical milestones : in the 1950s peter safar developed this emergency procedure to maintain airway , breathing & circulation

